 elings and marries Edgar Linton, a man of means who befits her stature. He
 athcliff vows to win her back.\n\nStarring: Juliette Binoche, Ralph Fienne
 s, Janet McTeer, Sophie Ward, Simon Shepherd, Jeremy Northam\n\nFilm relea
